<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>GST Invoice Template - Word</title>
<style>
body { font-family: 'Calibri', Arial, sans-serif; padding: 30px; max-width: 800px; margin: auto; font-size: 12pt; }
h1 { text-align: center; color: #1E3A8A; border-bottom: 2px solid #1E3A8A; padding-bottom: 10px; }
.invoice-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin: 20px 0; }
.seller-box, .invoice-box { border: 1px solid #333; padding: 15px; width: 48%; }
.buyer-box { border: 1px solid #333; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; }
table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; }
th, td { border: 1px solid #333; padding: 10px; text-align: center; }
th { background: #1E3A8A; color: white; }
.total-section { margin-top: 20px; }
.total-row td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }
.bank-details { border: 1px solid #333; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
.signature { margin-top: 50px; text-align: center; }
.footer { text-align: center; font-size: 10pt; color: #666; margin-top: 30px; }
</style>
<!--[if gte mso 9]>
<xml><w:WordDocument></w:WordDocument>
<![endif]-->
</head>
<body>

<h1>TAX INVOICE (GST)</h1>

<div class="invoice-header">
<div class="seller-box">
<strong>FROM (Seller):</strong><br>
[Company Name]<br>
[Address Line 1]<br>
[Address Line 2]<br>
City - PIN Code<br>
GSTIN: <strong>XXXXXXXXXXXXXX</strong><br>
State: [State Name]
</div>
<div class="invoice-box">
<strong>Invoice Details:</strong><br>
Invoice No.: <strong>[INV-0001]</strong><br>
Date: [DD/MM/YYYY]<br>
Place of Supply: [State Name]<br>
Reverse Charge: No
</div>
</div>

<div class="buyer-box">
<strong>TO (Buyer - Bill To):</strong><br>
[Customer Name]<br>
[Address Line 1]<br>
[Address Line 2]<br>
City - PIN Code<br>
GSTIN: <strong>XXXXXXXXXXXXXX</strong><br>
State: [State Name]
</div>

<table>
<tr>
<th>Sr</th><th>Description</th><th>HSN Code</th><th>Qty</th><th>Unit</th><th>Rate (₹)</th><th>Taxable (₹)</th><th>GST%</th><th>GST (₹)</th><th>Total (₹)</th>
</tr>
<tr><td>1</td><td>[Item Name]</td><td>XXXXXX</td><td>1</td><td>Nos</td><td>0.00</td><td>0.00</td><td>18%</td><td>0.00</td><td>0.00</td></tr>
<tr><td>2</td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td>0.00</td><td></td><td>0.00</td><td>0.00</td></tr>
<tr><td>3</td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td>0.00</td><td></td><td>0.00</td><td>0.00</td></tr>
<tr><td>4</td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td>0.00</td><td></td><td>0.00</td><td>0.00</td></tr>
<tr><td>5</td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td>0.00</td><td></td><td>0.00</td><td>0.00</td></tr>
</table>

<table class="total-section">
<tr><th colspan="8" style="text-align:left">Summary</th></tr>
<tr><td colspan="7">Total Taxable Value</td><td colspan="2" style="text-align:right">₹ 0.00</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="7">CGST (9%)</td><td colspan="2" style="text-align:right">₹ 0.00</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="7">SGST (9%)</td><td colspan="2" style="text-align:right">₹ 0.00</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="7">IGST</td><td colspan="2" style="text-align:right">₹ 0.00</td></tr>
<tr class="total-row"><td colspan="7">GRAND TOTAL (₹)</td><td colspan="2" style="text-align:right">₹ 0.00</td></tr>
</table>

<div class="bank-details">
<strong>Bank Details:</strong><br>
Bank Name: [Bank Name]<br>
Account Number: XXXXXXXXXXXX<br>
IFSC Code: XXXXXXXXXX<br>
Branch: [Branch Name]
</div>

<div class="signature">
<p>___________________</p>
<p>Authorized Signature</p>
</div>

<div class="footer">
<p>This is a computer-generated invoice. No signature required.</p>
<p>Generated by GST Calculator Hub | gst-calculator.com</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>